data.description: Nestled in the charming community of Dallas, Georgia, this custom-built 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is a true masterpiece of design and functionality. From the moment you arrive, you'll be captivated by its elegant facade and thoughtful details. This home is a well designed craftsman starting from the moment you step foot on the spacious flagstone front porch. You will see no expense was spared and this home has abundant detailed custom trim throughout.   Step inside to discover a haven of luxury and comfort, where designer colors and premium finishes abound. The living room being well designed with an open floorplan, a custom two story rock fireplace and a view of the woods and sunrise behind through the gorgeous windows. The interior is adorned with exquisite touches, including solid cherry cabinets in the kitchen and bathrooms, granite counters throughout, and upgraded designer doors that add a touch of sophistication to every room.  The heart of the home is undoubtedly the chef's dream kitchen, where nothing has been overlooked. Featuring double ovens, custom cabinets with soft-close hinges, and a beautiful tile backsplash, this kitchen is as practical as it is beautiful. Solid Oak hardwood floors flow seamlessly throughout the main level, adding warmth and character to the space.  The luxurious primary suite is a sanctuary unto itself, boasting a spa-like ensuite bathroom and direct access to the oversized deck, perfect for enjoying morning coffee or stargazing in the evening. Three additional bedrooms offer ample space and comfort for family and guests, while a laundry room (not just a closet!) on the main level adds convenience to daily chores.  Storage is abundant in this home, with tons of closet space, an extended oversized garage, and attic storage providing plenty of room for all your belongings. The high-efficiency furnace ensures comfort year-round, while cordless blinds with a lifetime warranty offer both style and functionality.  Outside, the delights continue with a private cul de sac lot that backs onto a large fenced-in backyard, providing plenty of space for outdoor activities and entertaining. Relax on the screened porch or expansive deck, or take a dip in the hot tub on the huge extended patio – the choice is yours.  This home also offers close proximity to the community pool, providing the perfect opportunity to cool off on hot summer days. And with a full basement already stubbed for a bath and bar or kitchen, wired for electricity and HVAC, the possibilities are endless for creating your dream space.  Don't miss your chance to own this extraordinary home – schedule a showing today and prepare to be impressed!  Home has a VA assumable loan at 2.25% to qualified buyer.
